於死者，處無期\r\n徒刑或5年以上有期徒刑；致重傷者，處3年以上10年以下有期徒\r\n刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/MLDM/110%2c%e8%8b%97%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c687%2c20211202%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"MLDM,110,苗交簡,687,20211202,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"苗交簡","JNO":"687","JDATE":"20211202","JTITLE":"公共危險"}